dark dwarves known as Duergar has made its way into Shades of Gray.
Like their surface cousins they are strong, though their evil ways have
changed them in other areas. Unlike their cousins, they are not known for
working stone and metal, something which has made them less hearty over time.
They have become more dexterous through centuries of thievery and deceit.
All Duergars are evil.
