0 LAST~
Syntax: {clast tell{x
Syntax: {clast say{x
Syntax: {clast gtell/group{x
Syntax: {clast channels/shout/gossip{x
Syntax: {clast sog/ooc{x
Syntax: {clast clan{x (for clan members only)
Syntax: {clast immtalk{x (for imms only)
 
   This command allows to see several last message. LAST TELL shows
your tells, both received and sended. LAST SAY shows say messages.
LAST GTELL or LAST GROUP shows group tells. LAST CHANNELS shows shouts
and gossips. LAST CLAN shows clan talks. LAST SOG shows message from
sog general line.
~
0 SHARPEN WEAPON 'SHARPEN WEAPON'~
Syntax: {csharpen{x <weapon>
 
   This skill allows to sharpen your weapon. Only blade weapons:
axes, daggers, swords - can be sharpened. Also you need sharpstone
(hold) for sharpen. Weapon which you like to sharpen must be in
your inventory.
   You have a little chance to make your weapon sharp for ever. 
Differently your level depends duration of affect. Vorpal, holy
and vampiric flags decrease chance of success. You must remember
that there is a chance to destroy your weapon.
~
